Most people who report calls from the dead where the recipient is  
there to take the call say that a short and usually very normal  
conversation takes place. Afterward, the person who got the call  
realized the caller was a dead person and is shocked, but during the  
call, they report barely even registering that something odd is  
happening.

Ann

